title: Slow cooker chilli with baked beans
ingredients: ['800g lean beef mince', '1 1/2 onions', '2 sticks celery, chopped', '2 cloves garlic, minced', '1 (600g) jar passata', '3/4 tablespoon cayenne pepper', '1/2 teaspoon dried parsley', '1 teaspoon salt', '3/4 teaspoon dried basil', '3/4 teaspoon dried oregano', '1/4 teaspoon ground black pepper', '1 tin baked beans']
